*Postaje* sve teže da se pridržavam svojih navika. (It is becoming harder to stick to my habits.)

Njegovo lice *postaše* crveno od srama. (His face became red from shame.)

*Postaše* im mnogo pitanja o njihovom odnosu. (They were asked many questions about their relationship.)

Kod nje je vreme *postalo* vrlo dirljivo. (Time became very precious to her.)

Ona je *postala* svesna svoje odgovornosti. (She became aware of her responsibility.)